Package com.flipkart.client

Class FlipFitAdminMenu

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.client.FlipFitAdminMenu
public class FlipFitAdminMenu extends Object
A client class that simulates an admin menu for managing gym centres and owners in the FlipFit application.
